{"title":"微信小程序图片下方空白解决方案","slug":"微信小程序图片下方空白解决方案","date":"2018-12-17T06:21:34.000Z","updated":"2019-04-23T07:55:20.585Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<p>小程序中在<view>中放入<image>时，image下边框和view边框中留有一段空白。如：<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;view class=<span class=\"string\">'card'</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;image class=<span class=\"string\">'card_img'</span> src=<span class=\"string\">'/img/water.png'</span> mode=<span class=\"string\">'widthFix'</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/view&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></image></view></p>\n<p>就会出现如下情况：<br><img src=\"/2018/12/17/微信小程序图片下方空白解决方案/image.png\" alt=\"pic\"></p>\n<p>解决方法：<br>图片设置垂直居中的格式<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">.card_img&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    vertical-align: middle;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}